  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="section-header fade-in">
    <span class="section-number">01</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">About</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-text fade-in">
      <p>A results-driven CRM Systems Architect & D2C E-Commerce specialist with <strong>9+ years of hands-on experience</strong> designing, implementing, and optimising customer relationship management systems across the full Shopify and multi-channel ecosystem.</p>
      <p>With deep expertise in <strong>CRM architecture, customer journey design, and marketing automation</strong>, I bring a rare blend of technical depth and commercial acumen — building automated lifecycle campaigns across Email, WhatsApp, SMS, RCS, and Web Push, integrating AI/ML-driven personalisation, and owning every touchpoint of the consumer journey from acquisition to retention.</p>
      <p>I thrive as an <strong>individual project handler</strong> — managing end-to-end CRM deliverables independently while collaborating fluidly with marketing, tech, and product teams to drive measurable retention growth and revenue impact.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-contact fade-in">
      <div class="contact-row">
        <span class="contact-label">Location</span>
        <span class="contact-value">Jogeshwari-E, Mumbai</span>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-row">
        <span class="contact-label">Contact Number</span>
        <span class="contact-value">8898390089</span>
